sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant UI
  participant API
  participant DB

  User->>UI: Enter credentials
  UI->>API: POST /login
  API->>DB: Find user
  DB-->>API: User record
  API->>API: Verify password
  API-->>UI: Token + user info
  UI-->>User: Login success

  User->>UI: Click Join
  UI->>API: POST /applications
  API->>DB: Save application
  DB-->>API: Confirmation
  API-->>UI: Status = Pending
  UI-->>User: Confirmation shown
